---
import Icon from './Icons.astro';
---

<section class="testimonials section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <p class="eyebrow fade-up">TRUSTED BY LEADERS</p>
      <h2 class="section-title fade-up">
        What Healthcare <span class="text-gradient">Leaders Say</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle fade-up">
        Join dozens of facilities that trust MedGuard for their generator compliance
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-grid fade-up">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="rating">
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          "MedGuard saved us during our AHCA inspection. Their digital portal had every document the inspector needed, organized and ready. We passed with zero citations for the first time in years."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">SM</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4 class="author-name">Sarah Martinez</h4>
            <p class="author-role">Administrator, Sunset Gardens ALF</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card featured">
        <div class="featured-badge">TOP RATED</div>
        <div class="rating">
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          "When Hurricane Ian hit, MedGuard was here within 2 hours to ensure our generators kept running. They understand that for us, power isn't just convenience - it's life or death."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">JC</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4 class="author-name">Dr. James Chen</h4>
            <p class="author-role">Medical Director, Broward Care Center</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="rating">
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
          <Icon name="star" size={20} />
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          "The bilingual team is a game-changer. My maintenance staff can actually communicate with the technicians. Plus, their compliance guarantee gives me peace of mind."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">RD</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4 class="author-name">Roberto Diaz</h4>
            <p class="author-role">Facilities Manager, Miami Medical Plaza</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust Metrics -->
    <div class="trust-metrics fade-up">
      <div class="metric-item">
        <div class="metric-number" data-count="50">50+</div>
        <div class="metric-label">Healthcare Facilities</div>
        <div class="metric-sublabel">Served in South Florida</div>
      </div>

      <div class="metric-divider"></div>

      <div class="metric-item">
        <div class="metric-number" data-count="100">100%</div>
        <div class="metric-label">AHCA Pass Rate</div>
        <div class="metric-sublabel">Zero citation guarantee</div>
      </div>

      <div class="metric-divider"></div>

      <div class="metric-item">
        <div class="metric-number">4hr</div>
        <div class="metric-label">Emergency Response</div>
        <div class="metric-sublabel">Guaranteed SLA</div>
      </div>

      <div class="metric-divider"></div>

      <div class="metric-item">
        <div class="metric-number">24/7</div>
        <div class="metric-label">Support Available</div>
        <div class="metric-sublabel">Always here for you</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background: var(--clr-bg-section);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .testimonials::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -50%;
    left: -10%;
    width: 40%;
    height: 40%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--clr-brand-teal) 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.02;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--clr-safety-orange);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--ff-sans);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--clr-brand-teal);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .text-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--clr-safety-orange) 0%, var(--clr-coral) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--clr-ink-muted);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Testimonials Grid */
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--clr-border);
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-2);
  }

  .testimonial-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--clr-safety-orange);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, white 0%, rgba(242, 92, 42, 0.02) 100%);
  }

  .featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: 20px;
    background: var(--clr-safety-orange);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .rating {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--clr-warning);
  }

  .testimonial-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--clr-ink-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    position: relative;
  }

  .testimonial-text::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: -20px;
    font-family: var(--ff-display);
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--clr-safety-orange);
    opacity: 0.15;
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--clr-border);
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--clr-brand-teal) 0%, var(--clr-brand-teal-light) 100%);
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--clr-brand-teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .author-role {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--clr-ink-muted);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Trust Metrics */
  .trust-metrics {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--clr-brand-teal) 0%, var(--clr-brand-teal-light) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-3);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .trust-metrics::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 30px,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 30px,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 60px
      );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .metric-item {
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .metric-number {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--clr-safety-orange);
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .metric-sublabel {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .metric-divider {
    width: 2px;
    height: 60px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  /* Animations */
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) forwards;
  }

  .fade-up:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .fade-up:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .fade-up:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  /* Mobile Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .trust-metrics {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .metric-divider {
      width: 100px;
      height: 2px;
    }

    .metric-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>